{"tid":1730300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致和理非的考驗 - 落街啦！","createTime":"2019-11-17T13:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T13:36:29.000Z","uid":260852,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"331ef538714cc12027b4927c2d53462eca68a940","tid":1730300,"uid":260852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得當初港島200萬人大遊行？<br />\n今晚理大勇武被重重包圍，<br />\n各區跪求開花，<br />\n跪求左四個鐘都未開到，<br />\n和理非們，你地仲記唔記得當初既勇氣同埋堅定意志？<br />\n200萬除18區，<br />\n每區都至少有10萬人，<br />\n勇武們已經出哂去，<br />\n和理非都要一齊落街先可以救到佢地，<br />\n和勇不割，和勇合作先會贏㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白和理非有自己包袱，可能會驚落街空無一人，<br />\n現請求你地對住窗大叫光復香港，<br />\n如果有人回應就落去啦！<br />\n當你仲係屋企嘆緊冷氣，<br />\n唔好唔記得理大勇武幫你擋緊子彈！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"bf117b9c076d87412985aaabb0d4531aa7dee00f","tid":1730300,"uid":260852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:09:22.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔甩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b77faa3d4909adae96dc5e8304eae0877ee0426","tid":1730300,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"325dd03e571318feee311498e2b181b850a763e9","tid":1730300,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"329d3db90953ef21fc549ff227873b8b718e3cfd","tid":1730300,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"反包圍呀"},{"pid":"6029ee8ee6938bfa1c87073862a602ff55d23367","tid":1730300,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"318d5c173c997a7803d83e5f463bde49fb2f5b45","tid":1730300,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"